WEBVTT


00:00:00.520 --> 00:00:04.000
The 2024 25 season sees the start of an

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.300
exciting new era for the UEFA Champions League,

00:00:07.320 --> 00:00:10.300
UEFA Europa League and UEFA Conference League.

00:00:10.840 --> 00:00:12.040
Taking part in the competitions,

00:00:12.040 --> 00:00:15.500
though remains open and based on sporting merit.

00:00:15.560 --> 00:00:16.320
For next season,

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:19.520
the current 32 team group stage will be replaced by

00:00:19.520 --> 00:00:20.360
a league face

00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:22.520
featuring 36 teams.

00:00:22.520 --> 00:00:25.460
In each of UEFA's three men's club competitions,

00:00:26.360 --> 00:00:27.800
each team will be drawn

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:29.460
against eight different opponents,

00:00:29.520 --> 00:00:31.820
two from each of the four seating pots,

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:34.280
playing four at home and four away.

00:00:34.280 --> 00:00:36.500
However, in the UEFA Conference League,

00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:39.020
each team plays only six opponents,

00:00:39.080 --> 00:00:41.780
one from each of the six seating pots.

00:00:42.280 --> 00:00:43.560
Teams that finish in positions

00:00:43.560 --> 00:00:46.980
1 to 8 qualify directly for the round of 16.

00:00:47.320 --> 00:00:49.320
Teams ranked 9 to 24

00:00:49.320 --> 00:00:51.920
must face each other in the knockout playoff round

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:54.780
to join the top eight in the round of 16.

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:56.520
Teams in positions

00:00:56.520 --> 00:01:00.980
25 to 36 are eliminated from all competitions.

00:01:01.680 --> 00:01:02.720
In the knockout phase,

00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:05.700
all ties are contested home and away,

00:01:05.720 --> 00:01:08.260
culminating in a single leg final.

00:01:08.560 --> 00:01:09.760
In the new league formats,

00:01:09.760 --> 00:01:11.840
every match, every goal,

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:15.500
every point and position in the ranking counts.

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:16.560
The new system

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:19.740
will ensure fast changing and unpredictable standings.

00:01:19.880 --> 00:01:22.720
More matches between equally ranked teams

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:24.600
competing for crucial points,

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:27.380
with fans able to enjoy top clashes

00:01:27.480 --> 00:01:29.840
right from the first matchday.

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:33.000
2024 A thrilling new future

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:34.940
a European club football.
